
<head>
    <title>Registracija/Login</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <h2>Prijava</h2>
                <hr />
                <p>Logirajte se i upravljajte sa Vašim računom na WebShopu TechHaven.</p>

                <form>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="usernameInput">Korisničko ime</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="usernameInput" placeholder="" />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group mt-4">
                        <label for="passwordInput">Lozinka</label>
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="passwordInput" placeholder="" />
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info btn-lg mt-4">Prijava</button>
                </form>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-1 offset-md-1 d-none d-md-flex">
                <div class="vr"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <h2 class="mt-md-0 mt-sm-4">Registracija</h2>
                <hr />
                <p>Registrujte se da bi vidjeli popuste i ostale pogodnosti koje Vam nudimo!</p>
                <form>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="usernameInputNew">Korisničko ime</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="usernameInputNew" placeholder="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group mt-4">
                        <label for="emailInput">E-mail</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="emailInput" placeholder="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group mt-4">
                        <label for="passwordInputNew">Lozinka</label>
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="passwordInputNew" placeholder="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group mt-4">
                        <label for="passwordRepeat">Ponovi lozinku</label>
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="passwordRepeat" placeholder="" />
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info btn-lg mt-4">Registracija</button>
                </form>
                <h4 class="mt-3">Registrujte se danas i bićete u mogućnosti da:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Olakšate i ubrzate proces kupovine</li>
                    <li>Budete nagrađeni za vašu kupovinu HavenCoinsima</li>
                    <li>Ostvarite popuste i razne ostale pogodnosti</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
